compartments.input:
PREFIX : <http://lumii.lv/ontologies/UnivExample.owl#>
SELECT ?courseName ?programName WHERE{
  ?OptionalCourse a :OptionalCourse.
  ?OptionalCourse :courseName ?courseName.
  ?OptionalCourse :courseCredits ?courseCredits.
  FILTER(?courseCredits < 6)
  ?AcademicProgram a :AcademicProgram.
  ?AcademicProgram :programName ?programName.
  FILTER(?programName = "Computer Science")
  ?AcademicProgram :includes ?OptionalCourse.
}

  ?AcademicProgram a :AcademicProgram.

}
